Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Buying Swimwear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so... We're like, really indulging\Nright now, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Free soda refills at a casual restaurant is indulging?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, we'll only get one\Nsummer vacation as 16-year-olds, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're wasting it by doing stuff\Nlike blowing liquid onto straw wrappers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.65,Mask,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: Mushoku means unemployed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,reading reference books on barnacles,\Nand listening to Mushoku Pu songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean "Teishotoku P," and it's not a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Reference books on barnacles\Nare also not a waste of one's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, still! Summer makes you want to\Ngo to the beach or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, doesn't it make you want to\Nget into a red-hot summer fling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'd say that, out of all the high school girls in Japan, you \Nhave the least business talking about a "red-hot summer fling."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would like to go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right, Robo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be barnacles there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What other reason would there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of our "upper-lower" ranking, we're\N16-year-old high school girls, and we're at our peak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Armed with the right swimwear,\Nwe'd be unstoppable, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Higashi-Murayama does not have an ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's just a short train ride to\NEnoshima or Kujukuri Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck, maybe we could go overseas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Overseas? That's a bit of a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, well, I've heard Japanese girls\Nget a lot of attention when they go overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go to Hawaii, or maybe Dubai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And how will this be paid for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't we have some rich girl in our class\Nwho owns a guest house or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of thing only happens\Nin anime or manga! Not in real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And if there were someone like that,\Nthey wouldn't be at Saijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We could do a raffle! Like the kind they\Nalways have in anime and manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, where someone plays and\Nthey luck out and grab the special prize!
