Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna go to the beach,\Nwe should get some new swimwear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The timing is perfect!
