Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they screwing with us?\NThe piggy bank?! We want the goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to sell it on Mericar for 30 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering the train fare to JUSCO\Nand what we spent on our bikinis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't we have just gone to the pool\Nat Hokuhoku-Seibuen Amusement Park?{oof the cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As we have already purchased said swimwear,\Nrather than going overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we simply go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be barnacles there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo, what's with this recent fetish\Nyou've had for barnacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I occurred to me I would like to confirm\Nthe urban legend regarding barnacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Urban legend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, d-do you mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl tripped in a rocky area\Nand landed on her breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, there was nothing out of the ordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But the next time she changed into her swimwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a crunching sound emanated from her chest area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-this is the one where she's got barnacles\Nall up on her boobs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No. And barnacles are not parasitic toward humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, the barnacles had infested\Nthe breast pads of her bikini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, that's scary as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This urban legend is not "scary."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Barnacles are a highly regarded food item.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The young girl took the hint, and was able to \Ntake those breast-pad barnacles and cultivate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As urban legends go, it is a success story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Success"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sell me those!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Nurtured on my Boobs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take 100 of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can raise our own boob-pad barnacles\Nand rake in the profits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Barnacle Swimwear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}I Raised These\N{\an7}Bred Off My Own Boobs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Robo helped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This will make me a high school entrepreneur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And my company name will be "The Barnacles, Inc."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not very inventive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely put it up three minutes ago,\Nbut it got reported and deleted. But, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with barnacles?\NIs it because they're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the "bikini" angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing reeks of something suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, they're barnacles so of course they'll smell "fishy," \Nbut they shouldn't come across as suspicious, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking I hadn't seen you at school recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but sure enough, you're just as moronic as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily! Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to have a guest house in Dubai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I own no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And why Dubai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm striking out with guys here in Japan, but I think\NI'd be hot stuff at some luxury resort in Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're unpopular in Japan, I can guarantee\Nyou'd be equally unpopular in Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then tell me how to get the guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Whether it's at some beach in Japan, the pool at \NHokuhoku-Seibuen Park, or even the banks of the Karabori River!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are several techniques for attracting men, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think even you, Tanaka-san,\Ncan employ the basic of basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By which I mean, THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which "that" is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the "Five-S" strategy of any popular girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Five-S"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I've heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the order that popular girls\Nseason food when they're cooking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugar, salt, sushi vinegar, soy sauce, and miSo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the other Five-S approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, what you say\Nat singles' parties to get the guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know that one! It was on TV the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on and say them then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sashimi for dinner?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shika rice crackers for a snack?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sushi rice sound good?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Spot me 1,000 yen, will you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way could there be a Five-S approach like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?! They all start with "S," right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You could never combat the Dark Soul\Nwith that sort of S!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, this has nothing to do with Dark Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about the Five-S method\Nof being popular with guys at singles' mixers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mixers," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in such wicked gatherings,\Nbut I know of the Fivefold S:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Salamander, defeated at my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Signatures of the dead I count as allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Stigma I must bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sounds of a world as it falls to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one was just "Stuff"? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If the setting is a girl who is popular at a research\Nlaboratory, I also know a Five-S approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I really want to hear this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, go ahead. What's the first S?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"So, want to culture some bacteria?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I need to hear this to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, it just hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our school has a pool up on the roof, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we ever use it for class?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:18.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Curse of Saijo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:19.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}The Curse of Saijo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:19.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Introduction
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Many years ago, a member of the Ping-Pong Club\Ndied an ignominious death just before a swim meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}After that, pool-related accidents regularly occurred, \Nuntil Saijo finally closed it down altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why a member of the Ping-Pong Club?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd understand if it was a Swim Club member, but this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the most frightening and\Nmystery-laden part of this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Saijo has had those stories\Nabout Seven Spooky Things for a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, the Anatomical Model in the Science Room,\Nor the Bach of the Music Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and The Running Nino-esque Guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck is "Nino"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinjiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.92,TL Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: Urban legend states that statues of 19th-century leader\N{\an7}Kinjiro Ninomiya will move at night
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll only find Kinjiro up through\Nelementary school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not likely to see a Kinjiro at high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:11:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes it scary - a Nino shows up\Nwhen he's not even supposed to be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And they travel in packs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there's Hanamaru-san of the Toilet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to the girls' toilet on the second floor and\Nknock on the door of the second-to-last stall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and call out, "Hanamaru-san!"\Na voice will respond, "I'm Shibasaki."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamaru-san! Hanamaru-san! Hanamaru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And if you just keep repeating saying\N"Hanamaru-san," then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: Hana is "Nose" and Maru is "Round"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your nose will turn round!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will never go back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.51,Signs,,0,0,0,,Yasaka Station
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It got late, while I was out having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Loli-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you're loitering about at this time of hour,\Nyou'll get taken away by some scary man, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A scary man...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Scary men
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! N-not you! I didn't mean you, Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, it's not like I'm\Nloitering about for fun, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my smartphone at school,\Nso I'm heading there to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, so that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! By any chance, are you\Nafraid of the school at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Plus, Grandma said that ghosts\Ndon't appear in front of good kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan, you're cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say I'm cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so angry... I'll tag along with you, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,R-r-really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This kinda situation is nice too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what? You're trembling? Lily, are you afraid too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trembling because it feels way too good...{Oh no we all know where this is going :^)}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What feels so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the second-floor women's restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Hanamaru-san of the toilet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. That's nothing but an urban legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, there was a noise from inside just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Th-there seems to be someone there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault if you get cursed by Hanamaru-san\Nand have your nose become knobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The second door from the back... I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamaru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kanade Ninomae! Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It appears that the lock broke, and for a moment there,\NI didn't know what would become of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you stuck in there since lunchtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I tried calling out for help several times,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but everyone just kept getting scared\Nand would run away, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, once you uncover the truth of something like\Nthe Seven Wonders, it's pretty much nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, in reality, there are\Nno such things like spirits and ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pablo Diego...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what is this?! What is it?! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}José Francisco de Paula Juan Nepomuceno...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}María de los Remedios...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Even if it's a ghost, if it's a cute girl, then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cipriano de la Santísima...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Trinidad Ruiz y Picasso ....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Majo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, everyone, at this late time of night...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that would be our line, you know.
